2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The ShapeFit algorithm used in the paper is a convex program and can be considered a machine learning method. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper deals with a bipartite location recovery problem and proposes a set of deterministic conditions for exact recovery, which can be considered as a data structures and algorithms problem. 
4. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper deals with the recovery of locations and structure, which can be considered as a computational geometry problem. 
5. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The ShapeFit algorithm used in the paper is a numerical method and can be considered as a topic in numerical analysis.
